title: In The Groove 2 songfiles for Stepmania
description:
This is the In The Groove 2 Stepfile and song pack for Stepmania. This is a VERY rare pack so if you play stepmania I highly recommend you get this pack while you can. As far as I know there aren&#039;t any music videos in this one, but as you can see from the size this is ALOT of songs. Even if you don&#039;t have stepmania you should download this just for the cool songs!

Requested by magus on Stepmania Online. Have fun dude!
